-Simple Summary of Your Recipe Code
This Python program is a Recipe Manager and Weekly Meal Planner. It helps users:

Register or log in with a username and password

View, add, edit, or delete recipes, including ingredients, cooking steps, and servings

Plan meals for each day of the week by choosing recipes

Generate a shopping list based on the weekly meal plan

Search recipes by name or ingredient

Save and load data using CSV files for recipes, ingredients, and users

The program runs in the terminal and guides the user step-by-step through menu options.
